      <hedline>
        <hl1>Other Disappointments</hl1>
      </hedline>
      <abstract>
        <p>Norma Fritz letter on July 20 article on the perils of online shopping</p>
      </abstract>
    </body.head>
    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>To the Editor:</p>
        <p>In ''Web Product Images Can Lie Like a Rug'' (July 20), Katie Hafner was shocked and disappointed by the reality of the rug she ordered online. She should see the surprises that Internet dating can bring. At least with an inanimate object you don't have to smile and hide your dismay.</p>
        <p>NORMA FRITZ  Brooklyn</p>
      </block>
